0and%20building%20large%20fulfillment%20warehouses%20instead%20of%20storefronts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20led%20to%20a%20perhaps%20surprising%20shift%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3A%20There%20is%20now%20a%20dearth%20of%20supply%20of%20convenient%20neighborhood%20shopping%20centers%2C%20and%20that%20is%20driving%20up%20the%20value%20of%20existing%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarge%20investors%20like%20Blackstone%20have%20noticed%20and%20are%20now%20betting%20on%20the%20lowly%20strip%20mall.%20Blackstone%20spent%20%244%20billion%20in%20November%20to%20acquire%20Retail%20Opportunity%20Investments%2C%20which%20owns%20about%2090%20shopping%20centers%2C%20most%20of%20them%20anchored%20by%20grocery%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackstone%20President%20Jon%20Gray%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20he%20believes%20the%20extreme%20distress%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-office-debt-investing-outlook-blackstone-jon-gray-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercial%20real%20estate%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20faced%20in%20recent%20years%20is%20beginning%20to%20ease%20up.%20He%20now%20sees%20opportunity%20in%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20were%20an%20investor%20in%20real%20estate%20after%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20you%20would%20have%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20And%20my%20guess%20is%2C%20if%20you're%20an%20investor%20today%2C%20the%20same%20thing%20will%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20an%20event%20hosted%20by%20Goldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20just%20the%20value%20driven%20by%20scarcity%2C%20an%20uptick%20in%20in-person%20shopping%20also%20bodes%20well%20for%20the%20shopping%20center.%20Foot%20traffic%20to%20grocery%20stores%20was%2012%25%20higher%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202024%20compared%20to%20the%20same%20time%20in%202019%2C%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20Journal%20reported.%20And%20there%20are%20many%20small%20businesses%20that%20still%20attract%20IRL%20shoppers%2C%20like%20coffee%20shops%20and%20nail%20salons.%20Flexible%20work%20schedules%20are%20also%20allowing%20residents%20to%20take%20quick%20shopping%20trips%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20Corl%2C%20head%20of%20New%20York-based%20private%20real%20estate%20group%20Cohen%20%26amp%3B%20Steers%2C%20wrote%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cohenandsteers.com%2Finsights%2Fthe-retail-renaissance-has-arrived-in-private-real-estate-investing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20September%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20investment%20market%20for%20open-air%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshopping%20centers%20amounted%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bretail%20renaissance.%26quot%3B%20Corl's%20firm%20bought%20a%20fully%20leased%20outdoor%20shopping%20mall%20in%20San%20Mateo%2C%20California%20for%20%24127%20million%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpen-air%20shopping%20centers%20are%20the%20only%20major%20property%20type%20that%20is%20experiencing%20an%20acceleration%20in%20rental%20rate%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Corl%20said%20in%20the%20blog%20post.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20a%20durable%20acceleration%20in%20earnings%20growth%20combined%20with%20relatively%20high%20current%20yields%20will%20propel%20shopping%20center%20investment%20performance%20for%20some%20time%2C%20a%20reality%20that%20the%20market%20has%20yet%20to%20fully%20recognize.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-investment-opportunity-shopping-center-strip-mall-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736110455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677998a89fc2c160094731d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-investment-opportunity-shopping-center-strip-mall-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Neighborhood%20strip%20malls%20are%20e