accident%20are%20Commandant%20Saurabh%2C%20Deputy%20Commandant%20SK%20Yadav%20and%20Manoj%20Pradhan%20Navik%2C%20according%20to%20the%20defence%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20ALH%20MK-III%20helicopter%20of%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20met%20with%20an%20accident%20at%20Porbandar%20airport%20runway%20in%20Gujarat%20at%20about%201215%20hours%20on%20January%205.%20The%20ICG%20helicopter%2C%20with%20two%20pilots%20and%20one%20aircrew%20diver%2C%20was%20on%20a%20routine%20training%20sortie%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20defence%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Dhruv%20chopper%2C%C2%A0which%20is%20operated%20by%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20was%20on%20a%20routine%20sortie%20when%20it%20crashed%2C%20said%C2%A0Porbandar%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Bhagirathsinh%20Jadeja.%C2%A0The%20chopper%20crashed%20near%20the%20runway%20and%20caught%20fire%2C%20visuals%20showed.%20The%20blaze%20was%20later%20brought%20under%20control%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20fire%20engine%2C%20said%20the%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20crew%20members%20were%20brought%20out%20of%20the%20chopper%20and%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Porbandar%20in%20a%20severely%20burnt%20condition%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20behind%20the%20crash%20is%20still%20not%20known%20and%20an%20inquiry%20has%20been%20launched.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20is%20a%20maritime%20law%20enforcement%20and%20search%20and%20rescue%20agency%2C%20with%20jurisdiction%20in%20India's%20territorial%20waters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indigenously%20designed%20and%20developed%20Advanced%20Light%20Helicopter%20(ALH-Dhruv)%20is%20a%20twin%20engine%2C%20multi-role%2C%20multi-mission%20new%20generation%20helicopter%20in%20the%205.5%20ton%20weight%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20months%20ago%20in%20September%2C%20three%20crew%20members%20went%20missing%20after%20the%20ALH%20MK-III%20helicopter%20fell%20into%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20off%20Porbandar.%20While%20the%20bodies%20of%20two%20crew%20members%20were%20recovered%20subsequently%2C%20a%20search%20continued%20to%20trace%20Rakesh%20Kumar%20Rana%2C%20the%20pilot%20in%20command%20of%20the%20mission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month-long%20search%2C%20the%20pilot's%20body%20was%20recovered%20in%20October%20off%20the%20Gujarat%20coast%20by%20the%20Coast%20Guard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chopper%20crashed%20while%20trying%20to%20evacuate%20an%20injured%20man%20on%20board%20motor%20tanker%20Hari%20Leela%2C%20nearly%2030%20nautical%20miles%20from%20the%20Porbandar%20coast.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20string%20of%20flaws%20were%20identified%20in%20the%20ALH%20Dhruv%20chopper%2C%20which%20is%20operated%20by%20the%20Army%2C%20Navy%20and%20the%20Air%20Force.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20certain%20design%20and%20metallurgy%20issues%20in%20some%20components%20that%20were%20identified.%20The%20scrutiny%20was%20carried%20out%20after%20accidents%20involving%20the%20platform%20that%20had%20forced%20the%20Army%20and%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20to%20ground%20their%20fleets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choppers%20that%20were%20grounded%20resumed%20their%20operations%20following%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20safety%20audit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%2C%20the%20IAF%2C%20the%20Army%20and%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20have%20a%20total%20of%20over%20325%20ALH%20Dhruv%20helicopters%20and%20all%20of%20them%20underwent%20technical%20checks%20following%20the%20incidents%20of%20accidents%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736095680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fmlj92ol8_dhruv-chopper-crash_625x300_05_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcoast-guard-chopper-crashes-in-gujarats-porbandar-3-dead-sources-7403835%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20pilots%20and%20an%20aircrew%20diver%20of%20an%20Advanc