20shocked%20to%20learn%20owned%20eight%20Multimixer%20milkshake%20machines%20%E2%80%94%20most%20restaurants%20and%20soda%20fountains%20he%20worked%20with%20only%20needed%20one%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20visited%20the%20brothers'%20restaurant%2C%20he%20was%20amazed%20by%20their%20%26quot%3BSpeedee%20Service%26quot%3B%20concept%20and%20saw%20promise%20in%20the%20restaurant%2C%20which%20had%20already%20become%20a%20success%20among%20locals%20who%20loved%20the%2015-cent%20hamburgers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20imagined%20scores%20of%20McDonald's%20restaurants%2C%20all%20utilizing%20the%20Multimixer%20machines%20he%20sold%2C%20and%20took%20his%20plans%20for%20expansion%20back%20to%20the%20McDonald's%20brothers.%20He%20offered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20restaurant's%20first%20franchisees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1955%3A%20Kroc%20opened%20the%20first%20franchised%20McDonald's%20restaurant%20in%20Des%20Plaines%2C%20Illinois.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224245%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mcdonalds%20downey%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e3ae3e55bc79c57903f1483%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222825%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20oldest%20operating%20McDonald's%20restaurant%20in%20the%20world%20is%20a%20drive-up%20hamburger%20stand%20in%20Downey%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EAllard%20Schager%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKroc%20opened%20his%20first%20restaurant%20on%20April%2015%2C%201955.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmcdonalds.gr%2Fen%2Four-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20first-day%20sales%20at%20the%20new%20location%20were%20%24366.12%2C%20the%20equivalent%20of%20about%20%244%2C300%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant%20differed%20slightly%20from%20the%20first%20burger%20joint%20opened%20by%20the%20McDonald%20brothers.%20For%20one%2C%20it%20had%20a%20new%20look%20created%20by%20architect%20Stanley%20Meson%2C%20who%20designed%20a%20modern-looking%20red-and-white%20exterior.%20Believing%20the%20roof%20appeared%20too%20flat%2C%20Dick%20McDonald%20introduced%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20now-iconic%20yellow%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20arches.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20oldest%20operating%20restaurant%20still%20featuring%20the%20original%20red-and-white%20design%20is%20located%20in%20Downey%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1961%3A%20Kroc%20bought%20the%20McDonald%20brothers%20out%20for%20%242.7%20million%2C%20kicking%20off%20a%20decade%20of%20massive%20growth%20for%20the%20brand.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22947%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ray%20Kroc%2C%20founder%20and%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20board%20of%20McDonald's%2C%20seated%20in%20his%20office%20in%20Chicago%20in%201978.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6776d92de5726ab18d0e4f60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22710%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERay%20Kroc%2C%20founder%20and%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20board%20of%20McDonald's%2C%20seated%20in%20his%20office%20in%20Chicago%20in%201978.%3Cp%3EUPI%2FBettmann%20Archive%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKroc%2C%20envisioning%20a%20larger%20future%20for%20the%20newly%20established%20McDonald's%20System%2C%20Inc.%2C%20the%20precursor%20to%20the%20McDonald's%20Corporation%2C%20secured%20the%20exclusive%20rights%20to%20the%20McDonald's%20brand%20name%20and%20control%20over%20all%20McDonald's%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKroc%20implemented%20strict%20standards%20for%20preparation%2C%20portion%20sizes%2C%20cooking%20techniques%2C%20and%20packaging%20to%20guarantee%20that%20McDonald's%20food%20would%20be%20consistent%20across%20the%20chain's%20many%20franchises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20created%20a%20training%20program%20for%20employees%20that%20would%20later%20be%20known%20as%20Hamburger%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201965%2C%20the%20company's%20stock%20was%20publicly%20traded%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20restaurants%20reached%201%2C000%20units.%20The%20brand's%20identity%20also%20changed%20a%20lot%20during%20the%20'60s%2C%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20Ronald%20McDonald%20as%20the%20chain's%20mascot%2C%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffish-sandwiches-ranked-mcdonalds-wendys-popeyes-burger-king-best-worst-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFilet-O-Fish%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20now-iconic%20double-arch%20%26quot%3BM%26quot%3B%20logo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1968%3A%20The%20Big%20Mac%20was%20added%20to%20menus%20nationwide.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222105%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22big%20mac%201977%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6776dcdae5726ab18d0e4ffc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221579%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProduct%20shot%20of%20a%20McDonald's%20Big%20Mac%20hamburger%20in%201977.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Groskinsky%2FThe%20LIFE%20Images%20Collection%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20iconic%20burger%20was%20created%20by%20franchisee%20Jim%20Delligatti%20of%20Pittsburgh%20in%201967.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Ffood-drink%2Fmcdonalds-big-mac-history%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Delligatti%20believed%20that%20McDonald's%20should%20sell%20a%20larger%20burger%20to%20compete%20with%20another%20local%20fast-food%20chain%2C%20Eat'n%20Park%2C%20which%20sold%20a%20%26quot%3BBig%20Boy%26quot%3B%20sandwich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201968%2C%20as%20the%20company%20planned%20to%20launch%20the%20burger%20nationwide%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-the-mcdonalds-big-mac-got-its-name%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%2021-year-old%20secretary%20came%20up%20with%20its%20name%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2F4338738fbc4ed82ddfcd5700c17d6ebd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAP%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20multiple%20executives%20and%20other%20employees%20thought%20the%20%26quot%3BBig%20Mac%26quot%3B%20name%20sounded%20silly.%20However%2C%20it%20stuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burger%20was%20an%20immediate%20hit%20and%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20chain's%20most%20popular%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1977%3A%20Kroc%20stepped%20down%20as%20CEO%20and%20took%20on%20the%20role%20of%20senior%20chairman.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222623%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ray%20Kroc%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6776e1cfe5726ab18d0e50d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221967%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERay%20Kroc%20is%20pictured%20in%20April%201979.%3Cp%3EAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKroc%20held%20this%20role%20until%20January%2014%2C%201984%2C%20when%20he%20died%20of%20heart%20failure%20at%20Scripps%20Memorial%20Hospital%20in%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20Kroc's%20death%2C%20there%20were%207%2C500%20McDonald's%20restaurants%20in%20nearly%2030%20countries%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20the%20company%20was%20worth%20%248%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-founder-ray-kroc-chain-timeline%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736089561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6776b9709de00e389eb41ccc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-founder-ray-kroc-chain-timeline%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ray%20Kroc%20transformed%20a%20small%20family-owned%20burger%20stand%20into%20McDonald's%2C%20the%20world's%20biggest%20fast-food%20empire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22emcdowell%40businessinsider.com%20(Erin%20McDowell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A351%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-founder-ray-kroc-chain-timeline%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhen%20There's%20Smoke...%26quot%3B%3A%20De%20Villiers%20On%20Reports%20Of%20Rift%20In%20Indian%20Team%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20India's%201-3%20series%20loss%20to%20Australia%2C%20former%20South%20Africa%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22AB%20de%20Villiers%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F699-ab-de-villiers-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAB%20de%20Villiers%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reacted%20to%20the%20rumours%20of%20a%20rift%20within%20the%20dressing%20room.%20India%20lost%20the%20series-deciding%20Sydney%20Test%20by%206%20wickets%20on%20Sunday%2C%20with%20the%20defeat%20ending%20their%20slim%20hopes%20of%20making%20it%20to%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20final.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20match%20at%20the%20Sydney%20Cricket%20Ground%2C%20one%20term%20that%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20was%20'Mr.%20Fix%20It'.%20A%20report%20in%20the%20Indian%20Express%20mentioned%20that%20a%20certain%20player%20in%20the%20team%20proposed%20his%20name%20for%20'interim%20captaincy'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20de%20Villiers%20suggested%20that%20these%20things%20aren't%20new%20in%20the%20sport%2C%20especially%20when%20a%20team%20is%20playing%20away%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20there%20have%20been%20some%20rumours.%20I'm%20not%20surprised.%20When%20there's%20smoke%2C%20there's%20fire.%20I've%20been%20part%20of%20dressing%20rooms%20where%20it's%20been%20hostile.%20Especially%20when%20you're%20away%20from%20home%2C%20you're%20missing%20your%20family%2C%20and%20you're%20not%20playing%20the%20best%20cricket%20of%20your%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20De%20Villiers%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cn