3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20all%20need%20a%20bit%20of%20both%2C%20and%20I'm%20sure%20the%20true%20virtue%20is%20found%20somewhere%20between%20the%20two%20%E2%80%94%20a%20middle%20ground%20your%20marriage%20of%20contentment%20and%20growth-orientation%20is%20perfectly%20suited%20to%20achieve.%20Finding%20this%20balance%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20tricky%20part.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20often%20heard%20people%20like%20your%20wife%20call%20themselves%20%26quot%3Bself-development%20addicts%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it's%20a%20fitting%20name.%20These%20self-development%20addicts%20tend%20to%20be%20dreamers%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20pot%20of%20gold%20they%20imagine%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20rainbow%20that%20gets%20them%20out%20of%20bed%20every%20morning.%20The%20image%20of%20themselves%20rocking%20toned%20abs%2C%20headlining%20a%20conference%20about%20how%20to%20get%20debt-free%20and%20build%20wealth%2C%20and%20finally%20becoming%20good%20enough%20to%20feel%20that%20emotion%20that%20comes%20naturally%20to%20people%20like%20you%3A%20content.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20you%20seek%20a%20compromise%20that%20both%20of%20you%20can%20live%20with%2C%20remember%20that%20this%20hunger%20for%20growth%20is%20essential%20to%20who%20your%20wife%20is.%20Like%20you%2C%20I%20tend%20to%20fall%20on%20the%20contented%20side%20of%20the%20dichotomy.%20So%2C%20I%20recognize%20that%20beyond%20the%20hassle%20these%20constant%20phases%20create%2C%20they%20can%20also%20feel%20like%20implicit%20criticism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20see%20this%20pain%20in%20your%20final%20question%3A%20%3Cem%3EHow%20can%20I%20show%20her%20our%20lives%20aren't%20broken%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20If%20your%20spouse%20is%20looking%20at%20your%20shared%20life%20and%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20improve%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20they%20are%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20good%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20must%20unlearn%20the