ss%20he%20cooperated%20fully.%20He%20was%20informed%20that%20he%20was%20now%20under%20%26quot%3Bself-custody%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20term%20that%20would%20lead%20to%2040%20hours%20of%20isolation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bahuguna%20described%20being%20interrogated%20via%20video%20calls%20by%20individuals%20impersonating%20law%20enforcement.%20%26quot%3BThey%20isolated%20me%20completely%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20contact%20anyone%2C%20pick%20up%20calls%2C%20or%20even%20check%20messages.%20They%20claimed%20I%20was%20under%20self-custody%20and%20that%20anything%20I%20did%20could%20be%20used%20against%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%2040%20hours%2C%20Mr%20Bahuguna%20remained%20trapped%20in%20a%20video%20call%20with%20the%20scammers.%20His%20gadgets%20had%20to%20be%20switched%20off%2C%20and%20every%20detail%20of%20his%20life%20was%20scrutinised%20by%20the%20scammers.%20He%20was%20even%20forced%20to%20show%20them%20every%20notification%20on%20his%20phone%2C%20under%20the%20constant%20threat%20of%20arrest%20if%20he%20attempted%20to%20communicate%20with%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20influencer%20recounted%20how%20the%20scammers%20manipulated%20him%20into%20sharing%20sensitive%20information%20and%20even%20performing%20questionable%20financial%20transactions%20under%20duress.%20%26quot%3BThey%20played%20good%20cop%2C%20bad%20cop%2C%20breaking%20me%20down%20mentally.%20I%20was%20crying%2C%20but%20they%20kept%20me%20on%20the%20call%20for%2040%20hours%20straight%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bahuguna%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20pick%20calls.%20I%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20message%20people%20or%20reply%20to%20their%20messages%2C%20let%20anybody%20in%20the%20house.%20They%20told%20me%20that%20if%20I%20tried%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20anyone%2C%20they%20would%20arrest%20me%20and%20harm%20the%20people%20I%20contacted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20his%20voice%20breaking%20as%20he%20recounted%20the%20emotional%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20coerced%20into%20completing%20suspicious%20tasks%2C%20including%20making%20bank%20transactions%20under%20duress.%20He%20was%20continuously%20told%20that%20if%20he%20didn't%20cooperate%2C%20his%20career%20would%20be%20destroyed%2C%20his%20family%20would%20be%20in%20danger%2C%20and%20he%20would%20be%20subjected%20to%20harsh%20treatment.%20%26quot%3BThey%20took%20my%20bank%20details.%20They%20took%20so%20many%20details%20of%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20told%20me%2C%20'Your%20parents%20are%20under%20threat%2C'%20and%20'If%20you%20try%20to%20contact%20anyone%2C%20we'll%20arrest%20you.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manipulation%20was%20relentless.%20Mr%20Bahuguna%20was%20instructed%20to%20send%20a%20screenshot%20of%20his%20every%20move%20and%20even%20had%20to%20pretend%20that%20everything%20was%20normal%20to%20his%20friends%2C%20who%20were%20concerned.%20As%20his%20friends%20contacted%20him%2C%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20reassure%20them%20that%20he%20was%20simply%20busy.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20were%20messaging%20me%20asking%20if%20someone%20was%20holding%20me%20hostage.%20This%20is%20not%20normal%20behaviour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled%20the%20confusion%20and%20fear%20his%20friends%20felt%20as%20they%20saw%20his%20increasingly%20erratic%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20he%20was%20instructed%20to%20leave%20his%20house%20and%20go%20to%20a%20bank%20to%20perform%20questionable%20transactions.%20%26quot%3BThey%20sent%20me%20to%20a%20bank%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20do%20some%20very%20fishy%20transactions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20other%20option%20but%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20the%20scammers%20even%20instructed%20him%20to%20check%20into%20a%20hotel.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20shaking%2C%20I%20was%20anxious%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20thinking%2C%20'What%20is%20happening%3F%20What%20is%20going%20on%3F'%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bahuguna%20recounted%2C%20revealing%20the%20toll%20the%20experience%20took%20on%20his%20mental%20state.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20literally%20crying%20and%20begging%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%2040%20long%20hours%20of%20isolation%2C%20manipulation%2C%20and%20fear%2C%20his%20luck%20turned%20when%20he%20managed%20to%20reconnect%20with%20his%20family.%20%26quot%3BMy%20sister%2C%20my%20friends%2C%20they%20were%20constantly%20trying%20to%20contact%20me%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20I%20saw%20her%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20describing%20how%20he%20saw%20a%20text%20that%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20arrest%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20scam%20prevalent%20in%20the%20country.%20He%20wrote%20in%20his%20caption%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20so%20lucky%20to%20have%20friends%20with%20such%20strong%20instincts%20who%20noticed%20a%20change%20in%20my%20behaviour%20even%20when%20they%20were%20getting%20'I'm%20okay'%20texts%20from%20me.%20They%20literally%20saved%20my%20life.%20Imagine%20if%20they%20hadn't%20come%20looking%20for%20me%20or%20looked%20for%20clues!%20I'd%20probably%20still%20be%20in%20that%20cyber%20arrest%20and%20would've%20lost%20all%20my%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20with%20these%20scams%20is%20if%20you%20buy%20one%20lie%2C%20they%20will%20tell%2010%20more%2C%20and%20those%20will%20be%20scarier%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned%2C%20urging%20his%20followers%20to%20be%20vigilant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDEcHE7asqtR%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDEcHE7asqtR%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C