r.com%2F6683ea79268f62ba18a685e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStefani%20Reynolds%2FBloomberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20may%20slow%20down%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20deregulation%20plans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20overturning%20of%20the%20Chevron%20doctrine%20in%20June%20limits%20federal%20agencies'%20power%2C%20complicating%20deregulation%20efforts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDeregulation%20delays%20could%20disappoint%20investors%20who%20have%20been%20pricing%20in%20less%20red%20tape%20since%20Trump's%20win.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotus-chevron-doctrine-bidens-climate-policies-at-risk-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20hinder%20one%20of%20the%20stock%20market's%20biggest%20reasons%20for%20rallying%20around%20Donald%20Trump's%20coming%20second%20term%20in%20office.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20election%20win%20in%20November%20excited%20Wall%20Street%20over%20the%20idea%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibecession-is-over-fake-politics-consumer-confidence-economy-feelings-sentiment-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20wave%20of%20deregulation%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20set%20to%20unleash%20gains%20for%20American%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20June%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotus-chevron-doctrine-bidens-climate-policies-at-risk-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecision%20to%20overturn%20the%20so-called%20Chevron%20doctrine%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20hinder%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20deregulatory%20agenda%2C%20strategists%20at%20Carson%20Group%20said%20this%20week.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chevron%20doctrine%20was%20a%20decadeslong%20legal%20precedent%20dating%20back%20to%201984%20that%20empowered%20federal%20government%20agencies%20to%20interpret%20laws%20when%20legislation%20passed%20by%20Congress%20was%20ambiguous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20precedent%2C%20set%20during%20the%20Ronald%20Reagan%20administration%2C%20was%20that%20courts%20should%20defer%20to%20the%20agencies%20rather%20than%20make%20their%20own%20judgment%20in%20such%20instances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20the%20precedent%20was%20overturned%20in%20June%2C%20courts%20are%20now%20dismissing%20federal%20agencies'%20interpretations%20of%20ambiguous%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20on%20full%20display%20earlier%20this%20week%20when%20the%20Sixth%20Circuit%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20struck%20down%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-net-neutrality%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enet%20neutrality%20rules.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three-judge%20panel%20specifically%20highlighted%20the%20downfall%20of%20the%20Chevron%20doctrine%20in%20their%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnlike%20past%20challenges%20that%20the%20D.C.%20Circuit%20considered%20under%20%3Cem%3EChevron%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20we%20no%20longer%20afford%20deference%20to%20the%20FCC's%20reading%20of%20the%20statute%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20decision%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarry%20Gilbert%2C%20investment%20strategist%20at%20Carson%20Group%2C%20said%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Friday%20that%20the%20Chevron%20doctrine%20was%20initially%20supported%20by%20conservative%20justices%20in%201984%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20it%20made%20deregulation%20easier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverturning%20Chevron%20was%20great%20(from%20a%20Republican%20perspective)%20when%20Democrats%20are%20in%20power%2C%20but%20it%20also%20makes%20deregulation%20more%20difficult%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20original%20Chevron%20case%20went%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Gilbert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Republicans%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frepublicans-house-representatives-election-win-majority-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eset%20to%20hold%20a%20trifecta%20of%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20White%20House%20and%20both%20chambers%20of%20Congress%20later%20this%20month%2C%20the%20overturning%20of%20the%20Chevron%20doctrine%20could%20come%20back%20to%20bite%20them%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20enacting%20policies%20aimed%20at%20loosening%20regulations%20for%20the%20private%20sector%2C%20according%20to%20Gilbert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20efforts%20to%20lighten%20regulatory%20requirements%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20met%20with%20waves%20of%20litigation%20that%20may%20take%20years%20to%20work%20their%20way%20through%20the%20court%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Gilbert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20have%20been%20swift%20deregulation%20policies%20enacted%20by%20President-elect%20Trump%20could%20now%20take%20much%20longer%20to%20play%20out%20as%20lawsuits%20inevitably%20make%20their%20way%20before%20the%20courts.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20worse%20off%20than%20the%20Reagan%20administration%20was%20before%20the%20Chevron%20ruling%2C%20because%20courts%20will%20be%20drawn%20into%20the%20messy%20process%20of%20delineating%20exactly%20what%20the%20new%20ruling%20means%2C%26quot%3B%20Gilbert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20December%20note%2C%20UBS%20said%20that%20after%20the%20overturning%20of%20the%20Chevron%20doctrine%2C%20certain%20efforts%20to%20cut%20spending%20could%20also%20be%20impeded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ruling%20also%20makes%20it%20harder%20to%20cut%20spending%20in%20areas%20that%20are%20well-defined%20in%20legislation%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20said%20that%20could%20impact%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-cuts-changes-elon-musk-vivek-ramaswamy-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enewly%20formed%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20seeks%20to%20significantly%20shrink%20the%20footprint%20of%20federal%20agencies.%20Eliminating%20entire%20agencies%20like%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20would%20require%2060%20votes%20in%20the%20Senate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20deregulation%20is%20still%20on%20the%20table%20during%20Trump's%20second%20administration%2C%20it%20could%20ultimately%20happen%20much%20slower%20than%20during%20his%20first%20administration%2C%20which%20could%20set%20the%20stock%20market%20up%20for%20disappointment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20make%20deregulation%20under%20the%20new%20Trump%20administration%20less%20robust%20than%20markets%20expect%20in%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20Gilbert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-chevron-decision-undermine-trump-stock-market-bull-rally-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736082901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677837cc44aa267a51f225e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fsupreme-court-chevron-decision-undermine-trump-stock-market-bull-rally-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20reversal%20of%20the%20Chevron%20doctrine%20%26quot%3Bmay%20make%20deregulation%20under%20the%20new%20Trump%20administration%20less%20robust%20than%20markets%20expect%2C%26quot%3B%20Barry%20Gilbert%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fsupreme-court-chevron-decision-undermine-trump-stock-market-bull-rally-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIVE%3A%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20helicopter%20crashes%20at%20Porbandar%20airport%2C%203%20killed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736081296000%2C%22visua