e%20is%20our%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Gema%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGema%20had%20earlier%20revealed%20to%20Sneha%20and%20Somu%20about%20their%20roots%20in%20Odisha%20and%20that%20they%20were%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20is%20well%20educated%20and%20conducting%20research%2C%20so%20she%20decided%20to%20locate%20her%20biological%20mother%20and%20I%20accompanied%20her%20to%20this%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Gema%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20their%20frantic%20search%20in%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20Gema%20and%20Sneha%20came%20across%20a%20retired%20teacher%20of%20Rama%20Devi%20Women's%20University%2C%20Sneha%20Sudha%20Mishra%2C%20who%20helped%20them%20find%20out%20the%20names%20of%20her%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20out%20about%20her%20parents'%20names%20from%20the%20house%20owner%20in%20Nayapally%20and%20later%20the%20names%20were%20verified%20with%20the%20police%20and%20the%20orphanage%2C%26quot%3B%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20Mishra%2C%20Sneha%20and%20Gema%20met%20city%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20Dev%20Datta%20Singh%2C%20who%20assigned%20the%20job%20of%20locating%20Banalata%20Das%20and%20Santosh%20Das%20to%20two%20police%20personnel%20Anjali%20Chhotray%20and%20Gangadhar%20Pradhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20found%20out%20that%20Banalata%20Das%20and%20Santosh%20are%20from%20Badamba-Narsinghpur%20area%20in%20Cuttack%20district.%20We%20have%20engaged%20police%20and%20panchayat%20functionaries%20to%20locate%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Inspector%20Anjali%20Chhotray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736078220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fut22kl58_sneha-enrique-vidal_625x300_05_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabandoned-20