tandard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fgovt-to-launch-another-round-of-pli-scheme-for-steel-sector-on-monday-125010500284_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rwanda-backed%20rebels%20seize%20key%20town%20in%20DR%20Congo%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736070836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F24c2%2Flive%2F97b8c540-cb47-11ef-bb10-a5f3e63456bb.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9wlzg7xn0no%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20the%20second%20town%20seized%20by%20the%20group%20in%20as%20many%20days%20in%20the%20mineral-rich%20North%20Kivu%20province.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A509%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9wlzg7xn0no%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9wlzg7xn0no.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc9wlzg7xn0no.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Zealand%20Changes%20Visa%20Rules.%20How%20It%20May%20Affect%20Indian%20Migrants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20persistent%20labour%20market%20shortages%2C%20New%20Zealand%20has%20introduced%20significant%20updates%20to%20its%20visa%20and%20employment%20requirements%20to%20streamline%20immigration%20procedures.%20The%20changes%20are%20aimed%20at%20simplifying%20immigration%20pathways%20for%20both%20employees%20and%20employers%20with%20adjustments%20to%20work%20experience%20criteria%2C%20wage%20adjustment%20and%20visa%20durations.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20overcome%20the%20storage%20of%20labour%2C%20the%20New%20Zealand%20government%20has%20lowered%20the%20criterion%20for%20work%20experience%20for%20migrants%20from%20three%20to%20two%20years.%20The%20move%20will%20allow%20competent%20workers%20to%20find%20employment%20more%20easily%20in%20New%20Zealand%20while%20still%20meeting%20the%20requirements%20for%20their%20positions.%20The%20new%20rules%20are%20expected%20to%20help%20Indian%20migrants%20seeking%20job%20opportunities%20in%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20has%20also%20introduced%20two%20new%20pathways%20for%20seasonal%20workers%20to%20stay%20in%20New%20Zealand--a%20three-year%20multi-entry%20visa%20for%20experienced%20seasonal%20workers%20and%20a%20seven-month%20single-entry%20visa%20for%20lower-skilled%20workers.%20These%20pathways%20are%20made%20to%20accommodate%20seasonal%20labour%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20median%20pay%20criteria%20for%20the%20Accredited%20Employer%20Work%20Visa%20(AEWV)%20and%20Specific%20Purpose%20Work%20Visa%20(SPWV)%20have%20been%20removed%20by%20the%20government.%20Under%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20though%20employers%20are%20obliged%20to%20post%20job%20opportunities%20and%20offer%20salaries%20as%20per%20market%20rate%20for%20the%20role%20and%20location%2C%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20needed%20to%20meet%20a%20predetermined%20salary%20criterion.%20This%20allows%20employers%20freedom%20while%20maintaining%20equitable%20worker%20remuneration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20migrants%20wanting%20to%20bring%20their%20children%20to%20New%20Zealand%2C%20AEWV%20holders%20must%20now%20earn%20at%20least%20NZ%2455%2C844%20annually.%20This%20minimum%20threshold%2C%20which%20has%20not%20been%20changed%20since%202019%2C%20is%20intended%20to%20ensure%20that%20migrant%20families%20can%20sustain%20themselves%20financially%20while%20living%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20New%20Zealand%20has%20extended%20the%20two-year%20visa%20period%20to%20three%20years%20for%20jobs%20which%20fall%20within%20the%20Australian%20and%20New%20Zealand%20Standard%20Classification%20of%20Occupations%20(ANZSCO)%20skill%20levels%204%20or%205.%20The%20current%20employees%20in%20these%20jobs%20with%20a%20two-year%20visa%2C%20who%20fulfil%20the%20requirements%2C%20may%20seek%20a%20one-year%20extension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployers%20are%20also%20now%20not%20required%20to%20follow%20Work%20and%20Income's%2021-day%20mandated%20recruitment%20period%20when%20posting%20job%20openings%20for%20skill%20level%204%20or%205.%20They%20only%20have%20to%20advertise%20and%20interview%20qualified%20applicants%20to%20show%20that%20they%20are%20making%20an%20attempt%20to%20hire%20locally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20reduced%20the%20domestic%20workforce%20criterion%20for%20some%20roles%20from%2035%20per%20cent%20to%2015%20per%20cent%20in%20order%20to%20address%20labour%20shortages%20in%20the%20construction%20industry%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20companies%20in%20this%20area%20to%20fill%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20this%20year%2C%20employers%20who%20are%20accredited%2C%20%C2%A0are%20also%20not%20required%20to%20complete%20the%20online%20training%20modules%20provided%20by%20Employment%20New%20Zealand.%20Instead%2C%20Immigration%20New%20Zealand%20will%20offer%20easily%20accessible%20resources%20on%20employment%20rights%20and%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20April%202025%2C%20migrants%20who%20want%20to%20transition%20from%20a%20student%20visa%20or%20any%20other%20work%20to%20AEWV%20will%20be%20given%20interim%20work%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20move%20that%20will%20benefit%20Indian%20students%20pursuing%20higher%20education%20in%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Wellington%20has%20modified%20the%20Post%20Study%20Work%20Visa%20(PSWV)%2C%20permitting%20students%20to%20stay%20and%20work%20for%20up%20to%20three%20years%20in%20the%20country%2C%20depending%20on%20their%20qualifications.%20The%20new%20rules%20will%20ensure%20that%20students%20who%20complete%20a%20Master's%20degree%20following%20a%20Postgraduate%20Diploma%20do%20not%20lose%20eligibility%20for%20a%20Post%20Study%20Work%20Visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736070240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fth2ilek8_passport-visa-generic-_625x300_23_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-zealand-changes-visa-rules-to-meet-labour-demands-know-details-7403982%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20persistent%20labour%20market%20shortages%2C%20New%20Zealand%20has%20introduced%20significant%20updates%20to%20its%20visa%20and%20employment%20requirements%20to%20streamline%20immigration%20procedures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-zealand-changes-visa-rules-to-meet-labour-demands-know-details-7403982%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRetirement%20In%20Your%20Hands%2C%20Playing%20For%20India%20Is%20Not%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit%20Served%20Big%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanjay%20Manjrekar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41124-sanjay-vijay-manjrekar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Manjrekar%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20retirement%20is%20a%20personal%20decision%20but%20the%20decision%20on%20whether%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20India%20playing%20XI%20in%20the%20future%20or%20not%20will%20be%20decided%20by%20the%20selectors.%20Rohit%20opted%20out%20of%20the%20fifth%20Test%20match%20in%20Sydney%20following%20a%20dismal%20run%20of%20form%20and%20in%20a%20candid%20interview%20on%20Day%202%20of%20the%20match%2C%20he%20addressed%20speculations%20about%20his%20future.%20In%20the%20interview%2C%20Rohit%20said%20that%20he%20will%20not%20be%20retiring%20anytime%20soon%20but%20Manjrekar%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20is%20no%20guarantee%20that%20he%20will%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20side%20if%20his%20form%20does%20not%20improve%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20there%20was%20also%20another%20reason%20why%20he%20was%20doing%20that%20interview.%20To%20clear%20the%20air.%20Somewhere%20I%20think%20Gambhir%20was%20getting%20all%20the%20credit%20for%20a%20brave%20call%20by%20leaving%20Rohit%20Sharma%20out.%20He%20wanted%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight.%20Let's%20be%20honest%2C%26quot%3B%20Manjrekar%20said%20after%20the%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20loved%20that%20interview.%20That%20first%20bit%20where%20he%20said%2C%20I%20couldn't%20have%20another%20out-of-form%20batter%20in%20the%20XI%2C%20and%20that's%20why%20he%20opted%20out.%20But%20there%20were%20some%20other%20emotions%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20players%20say%20is%20that%20%E2%80%98I%20will%20decide%20my%20future'.%20I%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20that.%20You%20can%20decide%20your%20future%20with%20regards%20to%20retirement%2C%20but%20somebody%20else%20has%20got%20the%20job%20to%20decide%20your%20future%20as%20a%20player%20and%20captain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20chairman%20of%20selectors.%20You%20have%20got%20to%20respect%20the%20hierarchy%2C%20however%20big%20you%20are.%20If%20the%20chairman%20of%20selectors%20is%20strong%20and%20he%20believes%20in%20the%20long-term%20health%20of%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20he%20has%20the%20power%20to%20decide%20whether%20your%20career%20should%20end%20now%2C%20or%20you%20get%20a%20few%20more%20matches%2C%20or%20one%20more%20series.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRetirement%20is%20in%20your%20hands%2C%20but%20playing%20for%20India%20is%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736070060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fdkveanag_s_625x300_05_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fretirement-in-your-hands-playing-for-india-is-not-rohit-sharma-served-big-warning-7404440%22%2C%22summary%2