20the%20NWS%20said%20in%20its%20latest%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20warned%20that%20areas%20from%20northeastern%20Kansas%20to%20north-central%20Missouri%20would%20see%20%26quot%3Bthe%20heaviest%20snowfall%20in%20a%20decade.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistorically%20Low%20Temperatures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20forecasters%2C%20a%20polar%20vortex%2C%20an%20area%20of%20cold%20air%20that%20circulates%20around%20the%20Arctic%2C%20is%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20extreme%20weather%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%2C%20this%20could%20be%20the%20heaviest%20snowfall%20in%20over%20a%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20coldest%20January%20for%20the%20US%20since%202011%2C%26quot%3B%20AccuWeather%20forecaster%20Dan%20DePodwin%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Btemperatures%20that%20are%20well%20below%20historical%20average%26quot%3B%20could%20linger%20for%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20jet%20stream%20diving%20southward%2C%20temperatures%20are%20expected%20to%20plunge%2C%20in%20some%20places%20to%20below%20zero%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20(-18%20Celsius)%2C%20while%20strong%20wind%20gusts%20will%20compound%20the%20dangers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mercury%20could%20sink%20tens%20of%20degrees%20below%20seasonal%20norms%20down%20to%20the%20US%20Gulf%20Coast.%20Before%20then%2C%20severe%20thunderstorms%20are%20expected%20across%20the%20lower%20Mississippi%20Valley%2C%20the%20NWS%20forecast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETravel%20Disruptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20major%20storm%20of%202025%20was%20already%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20travel%2C%20with%20Kansas%20City%20International%20Airport%20announcing%20the%20closure%20of%20its%20flight%20operations%20Saturday%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20rapid%20ice%20accumulation.%26quot%3B%20Flight%20operations%20resumed%20later%20after%20airfield%20runways%20and%20taxiways%20were%20treated%2C%20Kansas%20City%20mayor%20Quinton%20Lucas%20said%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParts%20of%20the%20eastern%20states%20of%20New%20York%20and%20Pennsylvania%20are%20facing%20%26quot%3Bheavy%20lake-effect%20snow%26quot%3B%20coming%20off%20the%20Great%20Lakes%20that%20could%20dump%20as%20much%20as%20two%20feet%20(61%20centimetres)%20there%2C%20according%20to%20the%20NWS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForecast%20company%20AccuWeather%20said%20Saturday%20that%20the%20lake-effect%20snow%20total%20in%20the%20region%2C%20already%20blanketed%20in%20snow%20this%20week%2C%20could%20top%20four%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20blizzard%20will%20rage%20across%20the%20Central%20Plains%20by%20early%20Sunday%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bwhiteout%20conditions%20will%20make%20travel%20extremely%20hazardous%2C%20with%20impassable%20roads%20and%20a%20high%20risk%20of%20motorists%20becoming%20stranded%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NWS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20capital%20Washington%20could%20also%20be%20blanketed%20in%20five%20inches%20or%20more%20of%20snow%2C%20with%20up%20to%2010%20inches%20possible%20in%20nearby%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20concern%20is%20freezing%20rain%20and%20sleet%20expected%20from%20Kansas%20eastward%20to%20Kentucky%20and%20Virginia%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20thick%20ice%20to%20coat%20roads%2C%20making%20travel%20hazardous%2C%20bringing%20down%20trees%20and%20electricity%20lines%2C%20and%20potentially%20leaving%20millions%20of%20customers%20without%20power%20during%20a%20cold%20snap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NWS%20warned%20that%20it%20expected%20widespread%20tree%20damage%20and%20%26quot%3Blong-lasting%20power%20outages%26quot%3B%20from%20Kansas%20to%20the%20central%20Appalachian%20Mountains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConditions%20could%20prove%20especially%20perilous%20in%20the%20Appalachians%2C%20where%20a%20deadly%20hurricane%20in%20late%20September%20devastated%20communities%20and%20ravaged%20multiple%20southeastern%20states%20including%20Kentucky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20those%20communities%20are%20still%20recovering%20from%20the%20effects%20of%20that%20hurricane.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20storm%20%26quot%3Bwill%20likely%20cause%20significant%20disruption%20and%20dangerous%20conditions%20on%20our%20roads%20and%20could%20cause%20significant%20power%20outages%20just%2024%20hours%20or%20so%20before%20it's%20going%20to%20get%20really%20cold%20in%20Kentucky%2C%26quot%3B%20Governor%20Andy%20Beshear%20told%20an%20emergency%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20governors%20of%20Kentucky%2C%20Missouri%20and%20Virginia%20have%20declared%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%20in%20their%20states%2C%20and%20they%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20warn%20residents%20to%20expect%20hazardous%20weather%20this%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736069580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F50vmar0g_us-winter-storm-_625x300_05_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsnow-ice-bitter-cold-massive-winter-storm-puts-much-of-us-on-high-alert-7404274%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Millions%20of%20Americans%20are%20bracing%20for%20a%20powerful%20winter%20storm%20that%20could%20bring%20blizzard%20conditions%20with%20the%20heaviest%20snowfall%20and%20coldest%20temperatures%20in%20over%20a%20decade.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsnow-ice-bitter-cold-massive-winter-storm-puts-much-of-us-on-high-alert-7404274%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Leopard%20Kills%20Blackbuck%20Deer%20Near%20Statue%20Of%20Unity%2C%207%20More%20Die%20Of%20Shock%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20leopard%20entered%20a%20jungle%20safari%20park%20near%20Gujarat's%20Statue%20of%20Unity%20and%20killed%20a%20blackbuck%20deer%20following%20which%20seven%20more%20deer%20died%20of%20shock.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20during%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20January%201%2C%20triggering%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20local%20forest%20department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20forest%20officials%2C%20the%20leopard%2C%20aged%20between%202%20and%203%20years%2C%20managed%20to%20breach%20the%20well-fenced%20boundaries%20of%20the%20park%2C%20which%20is%20located%20within%20the%20periphery%20of%20the%20Kevadia%20forest%20division.%20The%20park%2C%20a%20key%20attraction%20near%20the%20world's%20tallest%20statue%2C%20is%20surrounded%20by%20the%20dense%20forests%20of%20the%20Shoolpaneshwar%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%2C%20an%20area%20known%20for%20its%20leopard%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20cat%20reportedly%20entered%20the%20herbivore%20enclosure%2C%20where%20it%20attacked%20and%20killed%20one%20blackbuck.%20The%20remaining%20seven%20blackbucks%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20died%20from%20shock%20and%20panic%20following%20the%20attack.%20Forest%20department%20officials%20confirmed%20that%20all%20eight%20carcasses%20underwent%20post-mortem%20examinations%2C%20after%20which%20they%20were%20cremated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%20(DCF)%20Agneeshwar%20Vyas%2C%20overseeing%20the%20Kevadia%20division%2C%20explained%20that%20while%20leopard%20movements%20in%20the%20surrounding%20forests%20are%20common%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20recorded%20instance%20of%20a%20wild%20leopard%20entering%20the%20safari%20park.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20park%20is%20monitored%20around%20the%20clock%20through%20more%20than%20400%20CCTV%20cameras%2C%20and%20the%20leopard's%20presence%20was%20detected%20almost%20immediately.%20Security%20personnel%20were%20alerted%2C%20and%20their%20response%20caused%20the%20leopard%20to%20flee.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20still%20not%20known%20whether%20the%20leopard%20has%20exited%20the%20safari%20park%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%2