nal%20day%20of%20the%20series%20did%20help%20them%2C%20considering%20he%20took%2032%20wickets%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20he%20(Bumrah)%20bowled%20he%20seemed%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20and%20took%20some%20key%20wickets.%20So%20yeah%2C%20no%20doubt%20that%20(his%20absence)%20helped%20our%20chase%20a%20little%20bit.%26quot%3B%20Although%20he%20termed%20it%20as%20Indian%20team's%20internal%20matter%2C%20Cummins%20was%20a%20touch%20surprised%20with%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20decision%20to%20drop%20himself%20from%20the%20playing%20eleven%20on%20account%20of%20poor%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20you're%20always%20surprised%20when%20the%20captain%20kind%20of%20doesn't%20play.%20And%20you%20know%2C%20same%20with%20Ashwin%20retiring%2C%20but%20honestly%20it%20doesn't%20really%20affect%20us%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20just%20turn%20up%20and%20you%20see%20who's%20going%20to%20be%20on%20the%20team%20sheet%20and%20you%20play%20whoever%20eleven%20they%20put%20out%20there.%20Honestly%2C%20it's%20been%20very%20little%20conversation%20I've%20chatted%20with%20him%20about%20what's%20going%20on%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20termed%20the%20win%20against%20India%20as%20%26quot%3Bhuge%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Indo-Australia%20bilaterals%2C%20having%20lost%20twice%20at%20home%20previously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%2C%20it's%20a%20huge%20win%20in%20the%20context%20of%20this%20series.%20It's%20as%20big%20a%20series%20as%20you%20get%20to%20play%20at%20home.%20It%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20kind%20of%20see-sawing%20throughout%20the%20whole%20series.%20So%20to%20finish%20it%203-1%20to%20hold%20the%20trophy%20is%20an%20amazing%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B......%20and%20I%20think%20the%20extra%20layer%20is%20now%20securing%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20Final%20which%20was%20always%20a%20huge%20goal%2