ive%20collars%20for%20Pawsitivity%20and%20interacting%20with%20the%20dogs%20that%20Rimjhim%20and%20her%20husband%20Tushar%20would%20take%20care%20of%2C%20she%20softened%20a%20bit.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20I%20was%20earning%20a%20significant%20amount%20every%20month%20by%20working%20for%20these%20animals.%20It%20was%20only%20fair%20that%20I%20gave%20some%20love%20back.%20So%2C%20I%20began%20befriending%20and%20feeding%20them.%20Some%20people%20might%20not%20like%20it%2C%20but%20I%20do%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20%3Cem%3Edidi%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Rimjhim%E2%80%99s)%20company%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20work%20in%20fewer%20houses%2C%20and%20could%20spend%20more%20time%20on%20my%20own.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20lacked%20the%20knowledge%20of%20where%20to%20source%20the%20materials%20or%20who%20could%20manufacture%20the%20collars.%20It%20was%20Reena%2C%20her%20house%20help%20at%20the%20time%2C%20who%20stepped%20in.%20She%20suggested%20where%20they%20could%20find%20the%20necessary%20materials%20and%20mentioned%20that%20she%20had%20some%20basic%20stitching%20skills%20that%20could%20come%20in%20handy.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20worked%20together%2C%20and%20the%20very%20first%20batch%20of%20collars%20that%20we%20made%2C%20we%20made%20with%20her%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rimjhim%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReena%20Dhanak%2C%2035%2C%20from%20a%20small%20settlement%20near%20Indore%2C%20has%20her%20own%20unique%20journey%20in%20animal%20welfare.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20was%20always%20against%20having%20dogs%20loitering%20outside%20my%20house%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20them%2C%20but%20because%20I%20was%20scared%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20